 dust and dirt on her.  Glancing around noticing a few of the people in the bathing hut watching her, she decided to make a show of lowering herself into the tub.  With infinate slowly she eased into the tub and let out an audible sigh.  The hot water felt like the Elysian Fields on her sore muscles.  She quickly washed and after she was satisfied she was clean, she laid her head back against the tub and closed her eyes, enjoying her soak.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 217<br> <font color=#993300>(1/24/01 8:04:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=133.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/pleiade3/ehipp.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Warrior's Big Day</span><hr size=1> :::The Queen smiled as she saw Sartha go up and speak to the young initiate.  From her view...the exchange seemed to have put Quinn into a better mood.  So, Hipp decided it must have been good...whatever Sartha said.  She watched as Quinn went to the bathing hut...and knew that would be good for the young warrior.  As a cold wind blew a chill over her skin, she realized that she had yet to Hera.  And turned back into her hut, to prepare for yet another ride.  There was one last place she could think that Hera might be.::: <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
